name: Lost in the dark [2]
description: A mountain climber (14 years old) of Mount Guntur in Garut, West Java, has been missing for 5 days without supplies. missing since Sunday, September 19, 2021, has been found on Friday, September 24, 2021. The climber feels that he has only been lost for less than 1 hour and does not feel that it has changed days
